dct_title_s: Map of the Little Scioto River and Pine Creek Basins and adjacent Ohio River tributaries showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Little Scioto River and Pine Creek Basins and adjacent Ohio River tributaries
dct_description_sm: Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Little Scioto River and Pine Creek Basins and adjacent Ohio River tributaries and quality of underground water.
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
"Prepared by HENRY L. PREE, JR., Geologist, Ohio Division of Water"
Scale bar lower right corner of map.
